  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat the oven to 350°F (180°C).",
    "2. Cut the French bread into small cubes and bake until crispy.",
    "3. Cook the bacon in a pan until crispy. Set aside.",
    "4. In the same pan, add olive oil and sauté the garlic until fragrant.",
    "5. Add the vegetables and stir-fry until tender.",
    "6. Add the spicy stir-fry sauce and cook for 1-2 minutes.",
    "7. Add the cooked bacon, green onions, and French cheese.",
    "8. Season with garlic powder, salt, and pepper to taste.",
    "9. Serve the stir-fry over the crispy bread croutons.",
    "10. Garnish with additional green onions if desired."
